'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #3056] on 1 December 2000 at 2:27 pm'!"Change Set:		fixDebugDate:			1 December 2000Author:			Bob Arning- fix debug option on menu in SyntaxError to work in morphic"!!SyntaxError methodsFor: 'menu' stamp: 'RAA 12/1/2000 14:24'!debug	"Show the stack of the process leading to this syntax editor, typically showing the stack of the compiler as called from fileIn."	debugger openFullNoSuspendLabel: 'Stack of the Syntax Error'.	Smalltalk isMorphic ifFalse: [Processor terminateActive].! !